scraped_data.title: Saveetha Technology Business Incubator (STBI)
scraped_data.content_preview: Saveetha Technology Business Incubator (STBI) is a state-of-the-art incubation facility that has nurtured over 30 successful startups. STBI provides 24/7 access to prototyping labs, mentorship from industry experts, and connections to venture capitalists. Notable startups include TechMed Solutions, AgriTech Innovations, and EduSmart Platforms...
